data.description: **$10,000 seller concession to use towards closing costs, down payment, or rate buy-down!** 4 beds, 2.5 baths, w/ large bonus room (or 5th bedroom) AND a main floor office! Open kitchen/livingroom w/new wide plank vinyl floors. Large island w/gorgeous slab countertops, undermount sink, upgraded tile back splash, gas range, dbl oven & a walk in pantry. Primary bedroom has an ensuite 5-piece bath w/double vanity, tile floors, cultured marble counters & walk in closet. The large, fenced backyard features a covered patio, dedicated play area (or garden space), an HOA approved shed & custom built in grill station. Central A/C. 2 car garage + add parking for 5 cars! All of this is down a private drive on one of the largest lots in the community!
